businesses.name: Enso Osteopathy
businesses.business_details: I previously worked in a clinic for 5 years before deciding to open my own clinic. We opened Enso in Armadale in July 2019 and have grown steadily since. The challenge of owning a business has been an incredible experience and exactly what I needed. I am so proud of Enso and the clinic we have created.
businesses.product_details: We are an osteopathic clinic with the ability to deliver clinical pilates and small group rehabilitation normally. 1:1 rehab is now available. Osteopathy is a holistic form of manual therapy looking at the entire body, not just the area of complaint to get to the root cause of the issue. Treatment can include massage, stretching, manipulation and dry needling.
businesses.new_products: We are offering virtual rehabilitation over Telehealth.
businesses.headline: Osteopathic clinic delivering manual therapy to injured and aching bodies
